{
  "stem": "20021.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Not when I did it, but later on as everything became hopeless, as the only way to survive actually was either to go to Auschwitz with very few chances for survival or else try to pretend to be a non-Jew, or find a Pole which will hide you out.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now out of those three categories, those which found Poles that hide them out, sooner or later most of them didn't survive.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because the Poles will take their money.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when the money finished, they would stop hiding them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In other cases, they would do it simply out of fear.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In another case, they would tell a best friend or a neighbor or a relative, yes, I'm hiding out Jews.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And before they knew, everybody would tell a friend.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And before you know, the police would found out, so forth.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So very few survived.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Those which did what I did, had to have what they called looks, which means good looks, to have the kind of looks which suggest everything but Jewish.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The Poles had an image in their mind of-- of Jewish looks, you know.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And if somebody didn't fit that image, they find it very difficult to believe that he's Jewish.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And among those that did it like me, who were even very successful, also only a small percentage survive.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that was only luck, sheer luck.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in my case, probably the fact that I left Poland in 1943 in July.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Had I stayed for another two years, who knows?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I might have been caught.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Every day my chances were even-- whatever they were-- that I will be caught.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So it-- it was extraordinary luck.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Plus the-- the cunning, the schtick, the-- the game that you play, you know, and so forth.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
